---
title: Cal Smart Rosemary Turkey Meatballs with Roasted Squash and Peppers
description: Savoury, herby turkey meatballs adorn this hash-inspired bowl stuffed with roasted squash, peppers and a drizzle of mushroom pan gravy!. You won't believe this dish is on the lighter side!

